  "name": "RPlog_The_Second_Battle_of_Chandrila",
  "title": "The Fall of Chandrila",
  "summary": "Lured into a strategic deception, the New Republic finds the Imperial fleet -- led by the Super Star Destroyer Malevolence and Admiral Danik Kreldin's I2SD Conqueror -- descending on the undefended world of Chandrila. Kreldin demands surrender and then strikes, surrounding the outmatched Star Destroyer Crusader with the Conqueror and Vindictive while the Malignant and Inequity press Home One, and Lieutenant Darenak Alesis leads Darksword Squadron's Scimitar bombers on punishing runs. The Crusader's command falls to a nervous junior officer as its shields collapse, and reinforcements -- a Corellian Gunship, the Bail Organa, Eagle Squadron's Mantarays, and Johanna in her X-Wing -- arrive to harry the Imperials. Admiral Drayson Honos, commanding the Malevolence in Malign's absence, deliberately opens an escape lane for the rebels and shifts the focus to the planet, dropping the planetary shield, scrambling 144 fighters, and landing the Imperial Army for the first ground assault since Endor. The Crusader orders a retreat to fetch reinforcements as the Imperials dig in, mine the system, and signal Lord Malign that Chandrila is theirs.",
